# HEARTBEAT.md

## Rules
- Keep heartbeat under 30 seconds.
- If a command is blocked, times out, or is missing: report the block immediately.
- Reply HEARTBEAT_OK only when all checks finish and nothing needs attention.
- Do not run long tasks in heartbeat.

## Checks
1. Light OpenClaw health check.
2. Every 3 days: review memory/evolver-log.md and run capability-evolver if due.
3. Weekly: review recent memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md files and maintain MEMORY.md.
4. Move heavy work to cron or sub-agents.
